text: Memnun Suljagić (born 16 February 1966) is a retired Bosnian professional footballer and youth coach. As a player, he represented FK Sarajevo, and was a member of the 1998/99 title winning side. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina footballers Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina international footballers Category:FK Sarajevo players Category:Association football defenders
